    35. Miss Jessie Morris - Games &amp; P.E. - 1945? Worked at OGS and Castleford part-time.<br>
    36. Mrs. Mary Oldroyd - Games &amp; P.E. - 1945 to 1947<br>
    37. Miss Barbara Walker - Games &amp; PE - 1948 to 1951<br>
    38. Miss Betty Waddington - Games &amp; PE - 1951 to 1954<br>
    39. Mr. Cathcart - English, R.I., Games &amp; PE - 1951 to 1952<br>
    40. Miss Linley - Domestic Science - from at least 1935 to at least 1962<br>
    41. Miss Herbert - History &amp; Latin - from 1922 to 1948<br>
    42. Miss Dorothy Cashmore - English and French - 1949 to 1950, was the daughter of Canon Cashmore of Wakefield Cathedral.<br>
    43. Mr. Rook - Music - from ? to 1947<br>
